    "d. A person is better without an information resource.",
    "Answer: c. The fundamental theorem of biomedical informatics states that people are more effective when partnered with an information resource.",
    "The alternatives, which are to have no cooperation with information resources and people, or to have people assist information resources, are less effective.",
